<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Payment Failed - NovaGems</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 650px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 25px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #cc0000; /* red for failed */
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .info {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background: #ffeaea;
      border: 1px solid #cc0000;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .info p {
      margin: 6px 0;
      color: #7a0000;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    th, td {
      border: 1px solid #f5cccc;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    th {
      background-color: #cc0000;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 25px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .retry-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #008080;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .retry-btn:hover {
      background-color: #006666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>‚ùå Payment Failed</h1>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>
      Unfortunately, your payment for order <strong>#{{orderId}}</strong> was not successful.
    </p>

    <div class="info">
      <p><strong>Amount:</strong> {{currency}} {{amount}}</p>
      <p><strong>Payment Method:</strong> {{paymentMethod}}</p>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
    </div>

    <h3>üõçÔ∏è Attempted Items:</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Product</th>
          <th>Quantity</th>
          <th>Price</th>
          <th>Subtotal</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each items}}
        <tr>
          <td>{{this.name}}</td>
          <td>{{this.quantity}}</td>
          <td>{{this.price}}</td>
          <td>{{this.subtotal}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p>
      Please try completing your payment again by clicking the button below.
    </p>

    <a href="{{retryLink}}" class="retry-btn">Retry Payment</a>

    <p>
      If you believe this is an error, contact <strong>NovaGems Support</strong> for assistance.
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>¬© {{year}} NovaGems | All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
